## Goals

By the end of the hackathon, your team should have:

- A working RAG assistant that answers financial questions using locally-served models and locally-stored documents
- Experience with the full local AI development loop: chunking, embedding, retrieval, generation, and evaluation
- Benchmark results comparing retrieval quality, answer accuracy, and latency across different configurations
- Code and architecture you can take with you and reference later
